	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are any Genesis flash carts currently in production? I remember reading about one a long time ago that was rather clunky looking, could only hold a few games, and had a parallel port in the back for the connecting it to a PC. It would be nice have something more along the lines of the user-friendly Powerpak and SNES Powerpak.

		

		</td>
