	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Wow, I didn't think I get such a quick response! Nor did I expect there to actually be any <em>decent</em>, non-parallel port SEGA flashcarts. Sweet! 
<br />
<br />So it looks like its a toss up between Everdrive and Neomyth. 
<br />But is there anyone here with experience in dealing with either product that could tell me which plays Genesis/Megadrive games more accurately? I find it hard to believe that both carts support every Genesis game as they claim to. Also, am I correct in understanding that both carts support SEGA CD and 32X without needing the actual peripherals? That...can't be right, I think. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" /> 
<br />
<br />Thanks again, guys!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


